    "description": "Shards Between Us introduces two sisters on their coming of age journey. Begin as Glas, the younger child, as she juggles nurturing her own magic and supporting her unravelling family. A short, delicate experience approaching the sensitive subject of emotionally-unavailable parenting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/46cbba22125a3fa161e23210534cf47c.poster.avif?t=1768170894\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/46cbba22125a3fa161e23210534cf47c.webm?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/46cbba22125a3fa161e23210534cf47c.mp4?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cultivate Enchanted Plants</h2>Each sister summons their own magical plant, representative of their personality and their role in the family. Summon plants to traverse across their crumbling home, bringing each sister closer together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/758d5ddaf6885dac4221a0a31d3d6497.poster.avif?t=1768170894\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/758d5ddaf6885dac4221a0a31d3d6497.webm?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/758d5ddaf6885dac4221a0a31d3d6497.mp4?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow Together</h2>Like any family, these sisters will fight. Viola, the eldest, sets high expectations. Overcome their differences to unlock Viola as a playable character. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/dd0898e6cd66b535a41284fc8b9b978c.poster.avif?t=1768170894\" width=640 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/dd0898e6cd66b535a41284fc8b9b978c.webm?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2272410/extras/dd0898e6cd66b535a41284fc8b9b978c.mp4?t=1768170894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prune Away</h2>Begin to heal your inner child. Find peace through the story of emotionally-unavailable parenting based on lived experience.",
